column2: SELECT ALL sa.OBJID AS akari_ID, sa.RA AS akari_ra, sa.DEC AS akari_dec, sp.z AS redshift, sp.zErr AS err_redshift, sp.class AS class, sp.modelMag_u AS u, sp.modelMag_g AS g, sp.modelMag_r AS r, sp.modelMag_i AS i, sp.modelMag_z AS z, sp.modelMagErr_u AS uErr, sp.modelMagErr_g AS gErr, sp.modelMagErr_r AS rErr, sp.modelMagErr_i AS iErr, sp.modelMagErr_z AS zErr, n.objid, n.distance into mydb.final_output1# from MyDB.akari1# AS sa CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (sa.RA, sa.DEC, #) AS n JOIN dbo.SpecPhoto AS sp ON sp.specObjID = sa.OBJID
